></picture><div></div></div></figure></div><p>当然，粉丝们常常对他们偶像的流行形象怀有敌意，而社交媒体则因蔑视而蓬勃发展。但我仍然认为这些批评可能有道理。这并不是说阿贝拉不会唱歌——她显然可以而且唱得很好。甚至她听起来也不像怀恩豪斯。事实上，问题在于她听起来<em>确实</em>像怀恩豪斯，但听起来并不<em>完全</em>像她，这实际上比听起来根本不像她更糟糕。</p><p>这个问题类似于日本机器人学家 Masahiro Mori 在他 1970 年关于人类如何与机器人建立关系的文章中指出的问题。</p><blockquote><p><em>跳跃后 - 这件作品的其余部分，加上一个拨浪鼓包，其中包括：<br> - 麦卡特尼真的受到小石城九人组的启发而创作了《黑鸟》吗？一个答案！<br> - 历史上最成功的打击犯罪活动<br>- 如何降低生命风险<br>- 精彩的新播客<br>- 如果您还没有付费订阅，现在是时候了。听乔丹的话：</em> </p></blockquote><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F77ea814e-d5ab-4825-838a-a6c681f00f38_1326x708.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F77ea814e-d5ab-4825-838a-a6c681f00f38_1326x708.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F77ea814e-d5ab-4825-838a-a6c681f00f38_1326x708.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F77ea814e-d5ab-4825-838a-a6c681f00f38_1326x708.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F77ea814e-d5ab-4825-838a-a6c681f00f38_1326x708.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F77ea814e-d5ab-4825-838a-a6c681f00f38_1326x708.png" width="448" height="239.20